    "id": "f9a71847-fca5-480e-b5d8-4b540720d8cb",
    "sentence": "The economic research that I have discussed today demonstrates, rather, that the objectives of price stability and stabilizing economic activity are often likely to be mutually reinforcing. Thus, the answer to the title of this speech--\"Does stabilizing inflation contribute to stabilizing economic activity?\"",
