  {
    "id": "0f13b910-9c63-4165-8b01-fb024d98b19f",
    "sentence": "What we can do is remain vigilant to emerging vulnerabilities and build resilience to a variety of potential shocks.",
    "source": "Financial Stability: Resilience and Challenges",
