  {
    "id": "be72722c-76b2-4cc8-8ac4-739481d1a0a4",
    "sentence": "On the financial side, if U.S. current account deficits were to persist at near their current levels, foreign investors would ultimately become satiated with dollar assets, and financing the deficit at a reasonable cost would become difficult.",
