  },
  {
    "id": "7260eab9-253a-4bd9-b61d-ec9f4b4e89b4",
    "sentence": "They knew that then-existing arrangements for international cooperation were not up to that task.",
    "source": "The Financial Stability Board at 10 YearsâLooking Back and Looking Ahead",
