    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "30715584-c426-4c77-8bbd-fd0cbb16ae63",
    "sentence": "Certainly, the key monthly and quarterly economic data releases are the gold standard, but I also find useful information in real-time data, surveys, and contacts with participants in the economy.",
    "source": "The Economic Outlook and Path of Policy",
    "doc_type": "speech",
