    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "bcf9b013-73b8-409e-bdca-eebd3560ac22",
    "sentence": "Monetary Policy amid Uncertainty\r\nI'd like to turn now to monetary policy.",
    "source": "The Economic Outlook and Monetary Policy",
    "doc_type": "speech",
