    "hor": "",
    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "61f8ed90-9efd-4b40-b7c5-7e4fc5a9175c",
    "sentence": "The Federal Housing Finance Agency (FHFA) has also published a report that suggests Federal Home Loan Banks (FHLB) must assess risks related to climate and natural disasters \"on the FHLBanks' businesses, their members, and the communities they serve.",
    "source": "Reflections on the Economy and Bank Regulation",
