    "hor": "",
    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "8c44de03-28ed-4b51-b3c7-86ccd3db1144",
    "sentence": "There is a second broad type of approach in which many banks have entered into agreements with specialized companies that essentially act as middlemen, frequently described as \"data aggregators.\"",
    "source": "Where Do Banks Fit in the Fintech Stack?",
    "doc_type": "speech",
