    "top": "",
    "sen": "",
    "ten": "",
    "hor": "",
    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "e18d66ec-c303-4258-bde4-28e5ec62fcbf",
    "sentence": "They would raise the funds to purchase ABS through debt issuance and, most significantly for the proposal, the repo market, in which the collateral offered would be liabilities of the NFBs.",
    "source": "Comments on \"Regulating the Shadow Banking System\"",
    "doc_type": "speech",
