    "hor": "",
    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "0a7ec391-297b-46a0-95c7-6f7d5e13b92c",
    "sentence": "And having or developing those tools is essential to allow aggressive action to ease financial conditions as the economy heads into recession.",
    "source": "The Federal Reserve's Policy Actions during the Financial Crisis and Lessons for the Future",
