    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "b105886d-c264-4dae-8e51-e5ae4ada3996",
    "sentence": "However, core inflation remains elevated, and I continue to see upside risks to inflation.",
    "source": "Reflections on 2024: Monetary Policy, Economic Performance, and Lessons for Banking Regulation",
    "doc_type": "speech",
    "date": "2025-01-09",
