  {
    "id": "0bad4f26-224c-4a07-9cb9-773c7848b8f4",
    "sentence": "I expect that the persistence of economic slack, accompanied by stable longer-term inflation expectations, will keep inflation subdued for some time.",
    "source": "The Economic Outlook",
