  {
    "id": "738787aa-5c43-48a4-b70d-141b2b5c58c1",
    "sentence": "My sense is that market participants and other members of the public focus instead mainly on the timing of the next policy change or on how many policy moves will occur in a given year.",
    "source": "A View from the Fed",
