    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "850f685e-cd21-4708-ac50-3032d331642d",
    "sentence": "Given the lack of familiarity with front-end yield curve targets in the United States, such an approach would likely come into focus only after additional analysis and discussion.",
    "source": "Navigating Monetary Policy through the Fog of COVID",
    "doc_type": "speech",
    "date": "2020-07-14",
