  {
    "id": "d905de67-0aa9-45e0-a6c9-718859889e18",
    "sentence": "Capital surcharges\nIn his May speech, Governor Tarullo alluded to the possibility of liquidity-linked capital surcharges that would effectively augment the existing regime of risk-based capital requirements.",
    "source": "The Fire-Sales Problem and Securities Financing Transactions",
    "doc_type": "speech",
