    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "bba985a1-0eb1-4243-8267-cbcc02036829",
    "sentence": "Financial development involves innovations or liberalization of financial markets that improve the flow of information.",
    "source": "On \"Leveraged Losses: Lessons from the Mortgage Meltdown\"",
