  {
    "id": "44374d8e-b1b4-4c6a-b8e1-784d7ddf00c7",
    "sentence": "The Fed's efforts were among the earliest in creating timely measures of aggregate production.",
    "source": "Data-Dependent Monetary Policy in an Evolving Economy",
