  {
    "id": "eb3b6ded-5b3c-4248-92a4-af9f48f16c2e",
    "sentence": "While these studies allow for differences in the weighting of price indexes across different income groups, they rely on the same elementary price indexes for subcategories of goods and services. As a result, they may miss additional sources of variation in the inflation rates experienced by households at different income levels.",
